    "[Bob]: Sounds good, Alice.",
    "I'll start by checking the chests for sugar and an egg.",
    "If I don't find them there, I'll go look for sugarcane to make sugar and search for chickens to get an egg.",
    "Let's meet back here with the ingredients we've gathered.",
    "If we both end up finding some of the same ingredients, we can share them to make sure we have everything we need."
